- This project should be rewritten in Java
- You should use Freemarker, Spring, Gradle for more efficient development
- Use Tomcat as a WAS

-MVC pattern
-- model(modelMap)
-- view
-- controller
-- service
-- DAO
-- DTO

- Multilayered architecture
-- view layer(render view using provided model)
-- controller layer(http related tasks, access to service,
    pass model to the view)
-- service layer(DTO manipulation, caching, access to DAO)
-- DAO layer(local filesystem related CRUD operations)

